      },
      "date": "2024-02-26 03:25:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> This can be abandon since we moved to Xarray and we use its locking instead.\n\nI think we still need obd_dev_lock. Once you grab a ref from the Xarray, you drop all Xarray related locks. Another thread could still have a ref to that same device and try to access it at the same time.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
